snippet.title: Emilia Clarke Reveals What Jason Momoa Really Thinks of Amber Heard
snippet.description:
Emilia Clarke Reveals What Jason Momoa Really Thinks of Amber Heard
Johnny Depp and Amber Heard had a tumultuous marriage due to domestic abuse. Despite the fact that they had been dating for nearly three years before to marriage, their differences only became apparent after they married, putting them in risky situations. Despite the fact that they divorced within a year of their marriage, you'll be heartbroken to realise that one of their fingers was chopped and had to be sewed back now that they're being abused.
